Placeholder so git tracks the empty organisms/ directory ahead of
the §17.128 R3 strands. Real files land in R3a (shell organisms:
BurgerMenu, Breadcrumb), R3b–R3g (one strand per node kind: BSC,
Computed, Text, Workflow, Picture, URL), R3h-1/2 (modals split
across two strands). See docs/atomic-design-layout.md for the full
classification.
